Paper: hep-th/0008051

Date: 2000-08-05

Title: An Exact Black Hole Entropy Bound

Authors: Danny Birmingham and Siddhartha Sen

Comments: 6 pages, Latex, v2 minor re-wording, additional reference, to appear

in Phyical Review D (title changed in journal)Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D63 (2001) 047501

We show that a Rademacher expansion can be used to establish an exact boundfor the entropy of black holes within a conformal field theory framework. Thisconvergent expansion includes all subleading corrections to theBekenstein-Hawking term.